Serving this much food should be illegal.  Don't go to Claim Jumper if you're not hungry - your stomach will explode!  This is what I miss the most about the West Coast!  Get the Chicken Cobb Sandwich, the potato cakes, the potato cheese soup or the blue cheese wedge you'll be back at least 4x/week!

