Barcelona is what Scottsdale is all about.  The best place to go for drinks, listen to music and people watch.  And the happy hour lasts until around 9p!  My friend and I had about 10 berrs and I think our bill was about $30.  About 10 of us went for New Year's Eve 2006 we had dinner and entry to the club for $75/pp.  I love the outdoor patio.  The staff are very polite.  Its just a fun place to go!

